{"tid":2488293,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[西史]有無人覺得而家已經處於和平時期末期？","createTime":"2021-04-14T06:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:55:50.000Z","uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc152e1b17937fa83cb34ecd432e84d642ad0bf","tid":2488293,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"睇返過去200年 <br />\n1815-1914 不列顛治世<br />\n1914-1945 WW1, WW2<br />\n1945-          二戰後和平<br />\n<br />\n1945年到而家列強之間無咩直接衝突，<br />\n大型衝突都係代理人戰爭/內戰居多，<br />\n有無人覺得而家已經差唔多到臨界點？<br />\n<br />\neg 第一島鏈幾乎係自由世界既最前線，<br />\n直頭係現代巴爾幹半島，<br />\n台海同南海都好有條件開戰，<br />\n而且去到world war級數都唔係天方夜譚"},{"pid":"782022347096dd4e0beaadbc9eb0363c7b586924","tid":2488293,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"同埋睇返而家世界分成兩大陣營<br />\n北約 VS 中俄<br />\n越黎越似一戰前夕既三國協約同三國同盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3535b83fd4894461c04fae728830860c19917077","tid":2488293,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果打完仗無人得益唔會咁on9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c47b0ec027778f335354534521d180150edc042","tid":2488293,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"得兩個方向 第二次冷戰同WW3<br />\n唔想打仗既話第二次冷戰會相對好少少"},{"pid":"09b628a14a3f9b48ae7115c25a36ffe2df081542","tid":2488293,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"首先要有兩個陣營<br />\n一個發緊癲，一個鳩縮緊<br />\nWW1 WW2如是，WW3已經一樣"}]}